title: Ep. #77 | Catching Up: Kevin of THE BOYZ
description:
Joining Eric today is Kevin from The Boyz! Tune in for a casual conversation on pop culture (e.g. Black is King, Community, The Fresh Prince of Bel-Air), passive-aggressive tiger parents, and Kevin's advice on following your dreams!


Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave a comment, rating and/or review on Spotify, Apple Podcasts, Soundcloud, and YouTube.


Episodes are presented by @thedivestudios


Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at http://www.divestudios.io/daebakshow !
